nodes.text: Kevin Beentjes worked in the creation of the Rogues Gallery feature of Star Wars Insider, and contributes to the official Star Wars website (formerly the Star Wars Blog). Beentjes is also a Wookieepedia editor under the name of Wild Whiphid, and is an administrator of the Dutch Star Wars wiki, Yodapedia. In addition, he is an editor for the TeeKay-421 fanclub magazine.
